---
title: Quickfire Beef Enchilladas with Homemade Ranchero Beans
description: Patrick’s been trying out a few new Mexican dishes in the Fresh Kitchen of late and the main technique in tonight’s dinner has become a favourite. By mashing up the kidney beans instead of adding them whole, you suddenly add a rich, creamy texture to
sauces ... arriba!
